{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_01","textHome":"我是万年樱的传闻，无血型，年龄0岁。但因@为不能和别人像这样说实话，她们就让我回@答「是柊樱子，17岁」。因为还有很多不@了解的东西，如果可以介绍给我的话，我会@很开心。那样的话，她们一定也会开心的。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.8,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":1}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":12.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_17","textHome":"失去传闻的实体之后，我们还会在记载着故事@的书中继续存在。在那里，我们会经常找同@伴聊天。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_18","textHome":"最近的传闻，和以前的风格不一样了。因为是@以粗暴为前提被创作出来的，就算会在书中@相遇，性格也合不来。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_19","textHome":"外出时得到的新能力，现在正是运用的时候了@。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_20","textHome":"又学到了新的东西，也要告诉书本中的大家才@行。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":1}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_21","textHome":"白天好寂寞。她们都不在，学校里也无聊得很@。但是努力慢慢适应好了。习惯在外面的生@活，也是她们所期待的事情。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_22","textHome":"就算拥有知识，也会有很多应付不了的变故，@外面的世界真让人困惑。但我还是很高兴来@到外面，因为我能作为守护四人的传闻，自@由地行动了。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304300,"motion":1}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_23","textHome":"我明白，身为传闻，并非遵循自然规律而诞生@的生命，不应在这世界逗留。但是，我还想@见证她们的前途，所以让我再努力一下吧。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_24","textHome":"啊，我认识的人。经常来找我的话，说不准会@和我一样被当成不对劲的人。要是那样也不@要紧的话就来聊天吧。告诉我各种各样的事@。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_25","textHome":"早上好。这是早晨在学校互道的问候。虽然明@知如此，但看着大家都说出一样的话，心里@还是觉得很不可思议的。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_26","textHome":"我不吃午饭，因为吃不出味道来。而且她们也@说最好不要吃，不知道吃下的饭会到身体的@哪里去。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_02","textHome":"我是柊樱子，17岁。我只关心有兴趣的人，@所以可能帮不上你多少忙。因为我是内容已@经被决定了的传闻。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_27","textHome":"我的居所，樱花总在盛放，还有无休止的蓝天@。所以看着日落时的天空逐渐昏暗的样子非@常新奇。……啊，这就是心动吗？"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_28","textHome":"虽然明白犯困的道理，但却不了解这种感觉。@犯困的时候是什么心情？什么感受？迷迷糊@糊？还是昏昏沉沉？告诉我吧。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":11.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_29","textHome":"日出日落，人类也遵循地球的昼夜循环而生活@着，就像画出了一道圆。而我，一动不动。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304300}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_30","textHome":"嗯？有魔女的话就去吧。我并没有战斗的理由@。不过，如果那四位想让我打倒魔女的话，@我就会战斗，即使我并不是魔法少女。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.6,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":1}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_31","textHome":"如果想伤害她们，无论是谁我都不会容许。即@使明知自己没有胜算，我也会战斗到粉身碎@骨。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304300}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_32","textHome":"虽然学到了各种各样的至少，但还是有不明白@的地方。人为什么想活下去还要互相残杀呢@？我已经看腻了，没有什么感想。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_33","textHome":"怎么了？你是有事才来找我的吧？说说看，想@做什么？还是有什么话想说？抱歉，我不是@太明白。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":11.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_34","textHome":"了解了一些料理的做法和最近流行的东西，但@是没有付诸行动。因为我欠缺感性……虽然@也想培养，但是应该怎么做呢？"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":200}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_35","textHome":"对了，想看樱花的话，就来我家玩吧。我会让@樱花盛放着迎接你的。但是，禁止弄脏，禁@止偷摘。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_36","textHome":"稍微有点想出门，能陪我一起吗？我想尽量积@极地去接触外面的世界，帮上大家的忙。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":1}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_03","textHome":"｜我能到这件传闻的外面去了…？｜"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":10.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_37","textHome":"我正在和书本中许许多多的传闻说话。聊外面@的话题，大家都很开心，我也很开心。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_38","textHome":"啊，请注意。遇到关于我喜欢的人的事情，我@就不会那么讲原则了……"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_39","textHome":"说起来，在学校和一个白翼变得要好了。一@开始是被追踪采访了，后来说我是用作宣传@的好角色。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3043_00_40","textHome":"嗯哼哼，突然觉得很开心。啊，先不要动。就@这样看着你，心情就好起来了。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1,2]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":304300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304300,"motion":0}]}],"group_34":[{"armatureList":[{"animation"